Goal:
	This addon colorizes your input text in channels, 
	queries and/or DCC chats. 

Contact:
	Ahinu (ahinu.laman@gmail.com)

Installation:
	Use /addon.dialog, then click on "install addon" and search for
	"install.kvs" where the README is and load it.

Uninstallation :
	Use /addon.dialog, select "twinsinputcolor" and click on "uninstall".

